Ing "'''Don't Stop Believing'''" metung yang kanta ning [[United States|American]] rock band [[Journey (band)|Journey]]. Ing kanta minuna yang linual inyang [[1981]] king album ''[[Escape (Journey album)|Escape]]''. Ngeni, tuturing deng [[signature a kanta]] deng banda.

Ing kanta bantug ya king kayang lyrica at makapansin a [[Piano tuning|detuned]] [[piano]] pamuklat, at inustan ning [[All Music Guide]] bilang "metung kareng pekamasanting a pamuklat a keyboard riffs king rock."<ref>[http://allmusic.com/cg/amg.dll?p=amg&sql=33:4hzsa9ugr23d allmusic<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> Dakal a misinup a albums darala ne ing track (kayabe no reng ditak a pu'unan a Journey "pekamasanting a linual" ) ampong dakal a linual pasibayu ning [[Escape (album)|''Escape'']] tatala re ing track bilang "'''Don't Stop Believin''''" agiang ing tal a pamansag kayabe ya ing "g".

